# Cell2020     
material.heat = function(n){
  colorRampPalette(
    c(
      "#283593", # indigo 800
      "#3F51B5", # indigo
      "#2196F3", # blue
      "#00BCD4", # cyan
      "#4CAF50", # green
      "#8BC34A", # light green
      "#CDDC39", # lime
      "#FFEB3B", # yellow
      "#FFC107", # amber
      "#FF9800", # orange
      "#FF5722"  # deep orange
    )
  )(n)
}
